    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The collective body of courtiers, family members, counselors, officers, and attendants constituting the retinue of a sovereign or high dignitary.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
